Carthage came out of the north, snuck attacked me by snagging my unprotected workers (my fault, got over confident), and pillaged the road that was to bring dyes (my 1st luxury) to my cities. I abandoned mathematics (that I had just started on), and force scienced myself to iron working. Carthage came at me a few other times, but did not succeed in whacking a city or snagging another free set of slaves.<br />
